@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_onwzaw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.00 / tmp + 0.67) * (v2 + 0.69 / v2 + 0.15)) - v1)
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.35 + v1 + 0.64) - (v0 + 0.01 * tmp + 0.51)) * wp.sin(wp.cos(v1 + 0.83)))
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.abs(tmp + 0.77) * (tmp + 0.38 - tmp + 0.08)))
    v2 = v2
    v1 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
